      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! It drives like a dream and has been kept tucked away in a garage. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
