    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive study in mechanical purity. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls flawlessly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a torque-sensing M-differential. The chassis remains taut with zero bushing deflection, and the subframe has been structurally reinforced to exceed factory specifications. Meticulously maintained with documented valve adjustments and rod bearing service, this vehicle represents the zenith of naturally aspirated performance. The exterior and interior are in concours condition, showing no signs of thermal cycling or UV degradation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
