      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presents in showroom condition. The exterior retains its factory luster with a professional ceramic coating and zero rock chips or road rash. Inside, the Agate Grey leather remains supple and free of any bolster wear, smelling exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; all services were performed exclusively at Porsche authorized centers, with a full binder of records included. With no track time, no modifications, and a clean history, this is the finest example currently on the market for the discerning collector or enthusiast who refuses to compromise.",
